<h3>consequences?&nbsp;</h3>
<ol>
<li>Social : harmony and tolerance&nbsp;</li>
<li>Women : non consensual pornography 96% of deep fakes on internet , sexual objectification&nbsp;</li>
<li>Political : Sabotage reputation of political leader</li>
<li>Media : Credibility loose , trust erosion</li></ol>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Social media and internal security</h3>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Media and Social Media is a double edged sword which can increase polarization in the world but can also become a neutral facilitators of online communication</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><strong>Pros</strong>-</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal; margin-left:36px">
<li value="1"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Improved intelligence capabilities through actionable intelligence</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Support investigation</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Maintaining law and order- London riots 2011</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Delhi police online FIR facility for lost articles</span></span></li></ol>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><em>Other Non-Security Related benefits</em>-</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal; margin-left:36px">
<li value="1"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Facilitation of social movements such as - Jasmine Revolution, Arab Spring, Hong Kong Protest, India Against Corruption, etc</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Reinvigorated platform of governance where both citizen and government can communicate with each other directly. Due to this, governments have been more answerable, accountable and transparent to people.</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">At interpersonal level, social media has help people in remaining connected despite of distances.</span></span></li></ol>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><strong>Cons</strong>-</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal; margin-left:36px">
<li value="1"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Easy and accessible platform- increase in prevalence of fake news, eg, few years back the exodus of North-Eastern from Bangalore after the rumors that they are being targeted, post truth world, Yellow page journalism, paid news, intrusive marketing, etc.</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Propaganda- radicalization, misutilization Kashbook</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Incitement of violence due to rumors- WhatsApp rumors causing lynching in Manipur in 2018- as well as sharing of violent hate crimes such as Rajasthan man killing another person and sharing video through social media.</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Harassment of women on social media</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Identity Theft- hacking or fake profile.</span></span></li></ol>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><strong>Challenges</strong> in handling these Cons-</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal; margin-left:36px">
<li value="1"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Legal challenges- privacy, etc</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Accountability issues - inability to locate to source of rumor, Blue Whale Challenge, etc</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Jurisdictional challenges - criminal operating from outside</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Encrypted Messages- eg, Two way authentication in Whatsapp is preventing authorities to enforce accountability</span></span></li></ol>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;"><strong>Opportunities</strong>-</span></span></p>
<ol style="list-style-type:decimal; margin-left:36px">
<li value="1"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Robust cyber security framework</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Manufacturing of electronics within India</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Awareness about importance of cyber security among businesses and citizens</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Developing capabilities to track intrusions, tackle state sponsored attack</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Cooperation at international level. - Budapest Convention</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Locating server within India.</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;">Clear legal framework to punish wrong doers.</span></span></li></ol>